    <url>/2020/04/06/Untitled/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="利用beautiful-soup爬取贴吧首页所有的帖子主题和对应的作者名字（要求存到字典中）。"><a href="#利用beautiful-soup爬取贴吧首页所有的帖子主题和对应的作者名字（要求存到字典中）。" class="headerlink" title="利用beautiful soup爬取贴吧首页所有的帖子主题和对应的作者名字（要求存到字典中）。"></a>利用beautiful soup爬取贴吧首页所有的帖子主题和对应的作者名字（要求存到字典中）。</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup</span><br><span class="line">url=<span class="string">'https://tieba.baidu.com/f?ie=utf-8&amp;kw=%E7%BB%84%E8%A3%85%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91'</span></span><br><span class="line">headers=&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'user-agent'</span>:<span class="string">'Mozilla/5.0'</span>,</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">'cookie'</span>:<span class="string">'BIDUPSID=59C8B0FE6B100760F7B0D089371C33A4; PSTM=1584285175; BAIDUID=59C8B0FE6B100760D0FC40A9BD5768D7:FG=1; BDORZ=B490B5EBF6F3CD402E515D22BCDA1598; BDUSS=U11VE9VMzFXSnRpcWJaNnRDVlFPQVpBOU5HSWkxVHhxVjVyVmZXTDhYMTNkSlplRVFBQUFBJCQAAAAAAAAAAAEAAADuc0J6usO6w9G9Mjc2AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHfnbl53525ea; TIEBAUID=4a3c80e708873882ff358700; STOKEN=500725ae2ae1ffd2c8069c2b3fb4ebf5acdeac297c79f9a496976895e4bd13ac; TIEBA_USERTYPE=edaa8f29d135c86180e78060; bdshare_firstime=1584869303064; H_PS_PSSID=30975_1442_31118_21107_30906_30824_31086; delPer=0; PSINO=1; st_data=828a208d3e89752f2087f406d5332b3909509a1a2c7d9704dc36c92266a0c24dd3858db776ea984cf9014919dc519a6dbac8195057a72ef2f7339b22b2c385a4f47e3c3d2df0f7351e58db507464c66baae6a6170244cab5df7010c367e58789ff7b32c8ef559469e95880d160a1970dd78633a5b3df7bf51807d68cc12b3136; st_key_id=17; st_sign=f9bd3736; Hm_lvt_98b9d8c2fd6608d564bf2ac2ae642948=1584869304,1585030017,1585030155; Hm_lpvt_98b9d8c2fd6608d564bf2ac2ae642948=1585030155'</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">r=requests.get(url=url,headers=headers);</span><br><span class="line">r.encoding=<span class="string">'utf-8'</span></span><br><span class="line">soup=BeautifulSoup(r.text,<span class="string">'lxml'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">dict=&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Title=soup.find_all(<span class="string">'a'</span>,class_=<span class="string">'j_th_tit'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">Author=soup.find_all(class_=<span class="string">'tb_icon_author'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">dict=&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> value,key <span class="keyword">in</span> zip(Author,Title):</span><br><span class="line">   dict[key.get(<span class="string">"title"</span>)] = value.get(<span class="string">"title"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(dict)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
